reviews.review_text:
First Click ! Cool to be the 1st cat to scope out this quite decent audience recording—-> SHAKEDOWN ENCORE!

Matt V !! What UP!!? We used to trade the old school way through the snail mail. I am stoked to be coming across your work the next day with freakin’ zero views. I , too, uploaded something yesterday and it is sitting there with zero clicks : kind of a true bootleg 
Perhaps you’ll be 1st click on my item. PEACE AND LOVE ! Hit Me Worh Music 
https://archive.org/details/CHAPMANMASTERS14
